cationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c7c04c265"},{"id":"2bd4f2f368","type":"paragraph","text":"(十)反对用“团结——批评——团结”的方式作为阻止鸣放的盾牌。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c7c04c265"},{"id":"ec425168dc","type":"paragraph","text":"(十一)向一切偏听偏爱的大学生干部提严重抗议！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c7c04c265"},{"id":"75f99746b6","type":"paragraph","text":"(十二)大学生要求全面的马克思主义的三大部分的介绍，反对不考虑大学生思想水平，将大学政治课作片面简单的重复！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c7c04c265"},{"id":"5e216b37f2","type":"paragraph","text":"(十三)立即取消调干助学金，全面照顾有困难的同学，反对培养学生贵族。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c7c04c265"},{"id":"2163525000","type":"paragraph","text":"(十四)完全支持川大化学系三年级同学呼吁！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c7c04c265"},{"id":"fc92c1a0c8","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957年6月6日","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c7c04c265"}],"page":{"id":"3d4fcda290","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c7c04c265","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}